<br />
<br />
<div class="btn-group">

<p>Would you would like to create a TaskDeck for your organization?
  <a button class="btn btn-mini" href="/neworg">Create TaskDeck</button></a>
</div>


<p>If a TaskDeck already exists for your company/organization/group, enter the name and passcode of your organization in order to join it. 



<% end %>




<% else %>



